title: Godzilla Novels by Marc Cerasini
description:
Three Godzilla books written by Marc Cerasini 

Godzilla Returns - ignores the sequels and takes place sometime after the original movie. 

Godzilla 2000 - Has nothing to do with the movie of the same name. Includes Rodan, Varan and other monsters.


Godzilla at Worlds End - Takes place after Godzilla 2000. Includes Biollante, Gigan and others.

All are in the Epub format in English.
